27B4AD0D.Line7.2CDEB: The thicket rests. You did well. Now please, take your leave. I need to think.

8DC0338B.Line5.2CDEB: You need not say it. The wild magic has taken Mochrann from me as well. The druids were right to fear it.

FCC999B8.VoiceDir5.2CDEB: distressed, sad. Takes a breath to get herself together.
